title: Electricity prices for households in Spain 2010 - 2018 , semi-annually
summary: In general Euro cents per kilowatt-hour has rose over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2017_S2 and 2018_S1.
The highest Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, of value 23.83 was reached at Year 2018_S1
Minimum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour about 20.88 was reached at Year 2011_S2
